      "start": 681.73,
      "end": 684.85,
      "text": "네, 이 다음에 이어지는 장면은요."
    },
    {
      "start": 685.19,
      "end": 688.47,
      "text": "특히 그 왕실의 그 Sandringham House 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 688.69,
      "end": 690.19,
      "text": "그 별장에 도착을 했을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.19,
      "end": 693.39,
      "text": "There was a book on her dressing table."
    },
    {
      "start": 693.63,
      "end": 695.79,
      "text": "Yes, a very special book."
    },
    {
      "start": 695.87,
      "end": 698.93,
      "text": "바로 앤 블린이라고 제목이 적혀져 있었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.93,
      "end": 700.53,
      "text": "네, 실존 인물입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 700.79,
      "end": 701.09,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 701.75,
      "end": 702.89,
      "text": "She was a former queen."
    },
    {
      "start": 703.01,
      "end": 703.35,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 703.57,
      "end": 706.35,
      "text": "Very short-lived for three years."
    },
    {
      "start": 706.51,
      "end": 708.43,
      "text": "And she was executed."
    },
    {
      "start": 708.75,
      "end": 712.35,
      "text": "She was beheaded, accused of cheating on the king."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.61,
      "end": 716.85,
      "text": "But it turns out that the king was actually the one cheating on her."
    },
    {
      "start": 717.31,
      "end": 718.49,
      "text": "So, 정말 어이없는 상황이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 718.57,
      "end": 719.39,
      "text": "너무 어이없네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 719.65,
      "end": 724.05,
      "text": "And she finds this book, 다이아나, finds this book about her on her bed."
    },
    {
      "start": 724.21,
      "end": 725.21,
      "text": "무슨 의미일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.21,
      "end": 732.07,
      "text": "그러니까, 뭔가 무서운 일이 앞에 일어날 것 같은 그런 암시를 하는 게 아닌가."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.39,
      "end": 733.35,
      "text": "Yeah, is it a threat?"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.47,
      "end": 734.21,
      "text": "Is it a warning?"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.59,
      "end": 735.59,
      "text": "Who did this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.95,
      "end": 736.51,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 736.63,
      "end": 743.41,
      "text": "이렇게 누명을 쓰고 죽임을 당했던 어떤 여인에 대한 책을 다이아나가 손에 얻게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 743.67,
      "end": 745.53,
      "text": "And right now, 다이아나's situation,"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.89,
      "end": 746.81,
      "text": "this is 다이아나요."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.91,
      "end": 747.19,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 747.35,
      "end": 749.47,
      "text": "Her husband is cheating on her."
    },
    {
      "start": 749.53,
      "end": 750.67,
      "text": "Oh, I'm so scared."
    },
    {
      "start": 750.85,
      "end": 753.79,
      "text": "But her family is kind of, the royal family is angry with her."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.79,
      "end": 758.87,
      "text": "그리고 초반에, do you remember the scarecrow in the field?"
    },
    {
      "start": 759.31,
      "end": 761.13,
      "text": "그 자켓을 입고 있었는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 761.33,
      "end": 771.03,
      "text": "그 아버지가 입었던 자켓을 지금 put it on her mannequin에다가 입혀놓고 대화를 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 771.29,
      "end": 771.43,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.13,
      "end": 774.27,
      "text": "She's talking to her dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.37,
      "end": 774.61,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.79,
      "end": 775.61,
      "text": "Her late dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.61,
      "end": 783.15,
      "text": "Papa, didn't you tell me once that we Spencers were distantly related to Anne Boleyn?"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.33,
      "end": 783.67,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 784.03,
      "end": 787.13,
      "text": "아빠, 이러면서 mannequin한테 옷을 입혀놓고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.53,
      "end": 793.84,
      "text": "아빠, didn't you tell me once that we Spencers were distantly related to Anne Boleyn?"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.84,
      "end": 800.46,
      "text": "Spencers 가문이 Anne Boleyn의 Distantly Related, 먼 후손이라고 하셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 800.9,
      "end": 802.02,
      "text": "We're distant relatives."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.3,
      "end": 803.3,
      "text": "이렇게도 많이 얘기하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 803.74,
      "end": 804.64,
      "text": "지금 살아계셔도."
    },
    {
      "start": 805.04,
      "end": 806.3,
      "text": "We're distant relatives."
    },
    {
      "start": 806.54,
      "end": 808.02,
      "text": "I'm not sure how we're related."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.26,
      "end": 812.1,
      "text": "아, 우리는 먼 친척이에요라는 의미의 문장을 들어보셨어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 812.78,
      "end": 814.54,
      "text": "I read all about her."
    },
    {
      "start": 814.54,
      "end": 819.94,
      "text": "They even wrote a poem."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.48,
      "end": 822.84,
      "text": "심지어 시까지 남겼던데요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 823.26,
      "end": 827.57,
      "text": "이렇게 오늘 들으신 부분이 다 완료가 되었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 827.95,
      "end": 829.51,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm a little worried for her now."
    },
    {
      "start": 829.85,
      "end": 830.45,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 830.81,
      "end": 835.31,
      "text": "특히 아버지의 자켓에 대고 말을 하는 장면이 나올 때마다 저는 I fell for her."
    },
    {
      "start": 836.35,
      "end": 838.01,
      "text": "너무 안타깝게 보이더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 838.01,
      "end": 844.65,
      "text": "She misses her maiden family, her maiden name family, the Spencers, her dad, her childhood."
    },
    {
      "start": 845.01,
      "end": 848.37,
      "text": "Or she needed someone to rely on or talk to."
    },
    {
      "start": 849.03,
      "end": 850.29,
      "text": "저는 기대할 곳이 하나도 없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.37,
      "end": 850.71,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.71,
      "end": 851.31,
      "text": "이 집에서."
    },
    {
      "start": 851.41,
      "end": 851.99,
      "text": "좀 답답해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 852.13,
      "end": 852.41,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 853.15,
      "end": 854.75,
      "text": "한 번 더 확인해 보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 854.95,
      "end": 857.03,
      "text": "If I gave them to you, would you take them?"
    },
    {
      "start": 858.07,
      "end": 858.43,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 859.85,
      "end": 862.41,
      "text": "No, she couldn't possibly think of it, ma'am."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.65,
      "end": 863.87,
      "text": "Until there's a dress to go with them."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.77,
      "end": 865.71,
      "text": "Until it's all set."
    },
    {
      "start": 867.11,
      "end": 868.11,
      "text": "You know, all set."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.11,
      "end": 870.4,
      "text": "It's as if everything's already happened."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.68,
      "end": 875.17,
      "text": "Didn't you tell me once Louis Spencers were distantly related to Anne Balloon?"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.54,
      "end": 877.54,
      "text": "He hasn't read all about her."
    },
    {
      "start": 878.34,
      "end": 879.02,
      "text": "They haven't read a poem."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.02,
      "end": 885.11,
      "text": "Oh, 김성우님께서, 크리스님, 이번 주도 고생 많으셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 885.57,
      "end": 887.49,
      "text": "다음 주 월요일 아침에 또 뵐게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 888.13,
      "end": 889.79,
      "text": "Okay, be there or be square."
    },
    {
      "start": 890.35,
      "end": 891.25,
      "text": "I'll see you on Monday."
    },
    {
      "start": 891.49,
      "end": 895.47,
      "text": "네, 우리가 내용은 다크할지라도 it was so much fun with you."
    },
    {
      "start": 895.63,
      "end": 896.83,
      "text": "Oh, I hope we can have fun."
    },
    {
      "start": 897.09,
      "end": 900.33,
      "text": "I know it's a little gloomy story, but we can have fun here."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.43,
      "end": 900.95,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.95,
      "end": 903.83,
      "text": "Because learning, we have to have fun if we can learn."
    },
    {
      "start": 903.95,
      "end": 905.09,
      "text": "꼭 기억하시고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.11,
      "end": 905.79,
      "text": "재미있게 해야죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.89,
      "end": 906.37,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 906.57,
      "end": 907.77,
      "text": "기대되네요, 다음 주가."
    },
    {
      "start": 908.21,
      "end": 908.73,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 909.31,
      "end": 910.13,
      "text": "See you next week."
    },
    {
      "start": 910.23,
      "end": 911.11,
      "text": "기대 많이 하세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 911.23,
      "end": 911.59,
      "text": "Bye."
    }
  ]
}